  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Get ready to take part in an undercover operation to stop an evil plan to steal \"Ice Nine,\" a destructive computer virus. As Tom Carter, you'll perform a variety of missions that slowly unlock a conspiracy within the CIA. You have an arsenal of tactical equipment, including a sniper rifle, submachine guns, shotguns, night vision goggles, and more. Take down your artificial intelligence-controlled enemies in different environments, or challenge up to three of your friends in a deathmatch arena.",
